<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>NexaCore</title>

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #0a0a0a;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
    }

    header {
        padding: 100px 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0a0a, #111);
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 3em;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
        color: #aaa;
    }

    .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 15px;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
        background: #007bff;
        transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
        background: #0056b3;
    }

    section {
        padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .features {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 30px;
    }

    .card {
        background: #111;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        width: 250px;
    }

    footer {
        padding: 40px;
        color: #666;
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Internet. From Within.</h1>
    <p>Meet AirNode. Plug in and create your own network anywhere.</p>
    <a href="#" class="btn">Get AirNode</a>
    <a href="#" class="btn">Learn More</a>
</header>

<section>
    <h2>What is AirNode?</h2>
    <div class="features">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>📡 Cellular</h3>
            <p>Connects to mobile networks instantly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>📶 WiFi</h3>
            <p>Broadcast your own network anywhere.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>🔌 Plug & Go</h3>
            <p>No setup. Just plug in and connect.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Products</h2>
    <p>AirNode Go & AirNode Pro</p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>NexaCore Data</h2>
    <p>No contracts. No limits. Your data.</p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Why NexaCore?</h2>
    <p>Your device shouldn't depend on WiFi. Now it doesn't have to.</p>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 NexaCore</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
